text: Cynthia Akanga is a Togolese-French dancer, choreographer, artistic director and director of live shows. In 1998 she appeared in the musical "Notre-Dame de Paris". Since 18 April 2014 she has appeared on the second season of the show The Best, broadcast on TF1, presented by Estelle Denis and Christophe Beaugrand. ==References== Category:Togolese entertainers Category:French female dancers Category:French women choreographers Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
